### Flight API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api

### Test 1: Get all flights
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights

### Test 2: Get flights with departure station filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?departureStation=BUD

### Test 3: Get flights with arrival station filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?arrivalStation=LTN

### Test 4: Get flights for specific route
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?departureStation=BUD&arrivalStation=LTN

### Test 5: Get flights with departure date filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?departureDate=2025-07-09

### Test 6: Get flights with price range filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?minPrice=15000&maxPrice=50000

### Test 7: Get flights with bundle filter (basic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?bundle=basic

### Test 8: Get flights with bundle filter (standard)
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?bundle=standard

### Test 9: Get flights with bundle filter (plus)
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?bundle=plus

### Test 10: Get only available flights
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?availableOnly=true

### Test 11: Complex filter - BUD to LTN, available, basic bundle, max 25000 HUF
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?departureStation=BUD&arrivalStation=LTN&availableOnly=true&bundle=basic&maxPrice=25000

### Test 12: Complex filter - departure date with price range
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights?departureDate=2025-07-09&minPrice=20000&maxPrice=40000

### Test 13: Get flights by specific route (BUD -> LTN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights/route/BUD/LTN

### Test 14: Get flights by specific route (LTN -> BUD)
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights/route/LTN/BUD

### Test 15: Get flights by specific route (case insensitive test)
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights/route/bud/ltn

### Test 16: Get flights by specific route (non-existent route)
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights/route/NYC/LAX

### Test 17: Get all flights from/to BUD station
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights/station/BUD

### Test 18: Get all flights from/to LTN station
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights/station/LTN

### Test 19: Get flights from/to non-existent station
GET {{baseUrl}}/flights/station/XYZ
